# Component Types
enforce prop interfaces
require event typing
implement ref types
enforce children types
require context typing
implement hook types

# Props Pattern
enforce prop validation
require default props
implement prop spreading
enforce prop destruction
require memo usage
implement callback typing

# State Management
enforce reducer types
require action types
implement context types
enforce selector types
require store typing
implement effect types

# Component Patterns
enforce functional components
require pure components
implement HOC types
enforce render props
require component composition
implement error boundaries

# Anti-Patterns
prevent any props
avoid implicit returns
prevent prop drilling
avoid type assertions
prevent default exports
enforce named exports